@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@
+---
+title: Daemon Auto-Retry For Allowlisted Terminal Markers
+date: 2026-07-11T13:19:34Z
+tags: [daemon, auto-retry, markers]
+---
+
+Documented the new [[modules/daemon]] `Hive::Daemon::AutoRetry` path: the
+daemon can evaluate parked terminal `ERROR` markers for the fixed v1 Codex auth
+and Claude launcher recovery classes, run health probes and safety guards, and
+enqueue the same manual `hive markers clear` plus same-stage `hive run` sequence
+through `DispatchRequestQueue`. The page now records that
+`daemon.auto_retry.enabled: false` disables evaluation before probes and that
+negative `auto_retry_decision` audit records are throttled by task/stage/reason,
+rationale, and health fingerprint.
